          <strong><a title="复制本帖链接" id="postnum6510" href="javascript:;" onclick="setCopy('http://www.bazhongshengku.com/redirect.php?goto=findpost&amp;ptid=9779&amp;pid=6510', '帖子地址已经复制到剪贴板')"><em>51</em><sup>#</sup></a> <em class="rpostno" title="跳转到指定楼层">跳转到 <input id="rpostnovalue" size="3" type="text" class="txtarea" onkeydown="if(event.keyCode==13) {$('rpostnobtn').click();return false;}" /><span id="rpostnobtn" onclick="window.location='redirect.php?ptid=9779&amp;ordertype=0&amp;postno='+$('rpostnovalue').value">&raquo;</span></em> </strong> 
