            <img class="authicon" id="authicon6518" src="images/common/online_member.gif" onclick="showauthor(this, 'userinfo6518');" /> 
            <em id="authorposton6518">发表于 2011-6-21 19:53</em> | 
            <a href="viewthread.php?tid=9779&amp;page=2&amp;authorid=61" rel="nofollow">只看该作者</a> 
